cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.CL 

The paper proposes a new task of generating a sequence of images from a multi-sentence paragraph, which involves understanding the context and generating consistent images. This task is related to computer vision (cs.CV) as it involves image generation, artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as it involves understanding the context, and machine learning (cs.LG) as it proposes a new model. Additionally, the paper mentions modifying existing datasets, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM), and human evaluation, which is related to natural language processing (cs.CL).
